State ex rel. Demellweek
v.
Indus. Comm. 2018-0499 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 16, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

On application for dismissal of appellant Lowe's Home Centers, L.L.C. Application granted. Appeal of appellant Lowe's Home Centers, L.L.C., dismissed. Appeal of appellant Industrial Commission of Ohio remains pending.
